Package Implementation

Class ParentalControls

java.lang.Object
Implementation.DataManager
Implementation.ParentalControls
public class ParentalControls extends Implementation.DataManager
The ParentalControls class extends DataManager to manage parental control settings for players, including playtime limits and playtime statistics.

      public int findRow(String playerId)

      Parameters:

      Returns:
